Surgical treatment of insulinoma. The paper summarizes experience with diagnosis and surgical treatment of insulinomas of the pancreas. Experience with three patients subdued to surgical treatment at the Department of Surgery of F.D. Roosevelt Hospital in Bansk√° Bystrica confirm the rules of effective treatment of insulinomas: importance of neurological symptoms in early diagnosis, importance of angiography as the best method for localization of insulinomas in comparison with ultrasonography and CT. In addition, algorithm of the surgical treatment of insulinomas together with the specificity of the surgical technique were confirmed.